[6] India (Kerala)
Date: Tue 19 Jul 2022 10:53 AM (IST)
Source: WION [edited]
https://www.wionews.com/videos/india-reports-second-case-of-monkeypox-special-alert-in-5-districts-of-kerala-498709


India has confirmed its 2nd case of monkeypox infection just 5 days after it detected its 1st. The 2nd case has also been detected from the southern Indian state of Kerala where the 1st case was reported on 14 Jul [2022].

